## Final Checklist

Before saving:

* [ ] New row added to CSV
* [ ] Correct semicolon format used
* [ ] City exists in CITY_LL
* [ ] Category names are correct
* [ ] Website starts with https://
* [ ] File tested in browser

---

## Notes for Non-Coders

Most updates only require editing the `CSV` section.

Only edit `CITY_LL` when adding a new city.
